                            <comment id="13175443" author="azaroth" created="Fri, 23 Dec 2011 14:28:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Generally looks good.&lt;br/&gt;
A couple of comments:&lt;br/&gt;
Is the modification to HiveColumnarLoader.java intended and related to this patch?&lt;br/&gt;
Could you delete, rather than comment, the code that you removed in the path creation?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175521" author="thw" created="Fri, 23 Dec 2011 17:56:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated patch. The Hive ColumnarStruct API has changed (getField no longer has a  org.apache.hadoop.io.Text nullSequence parameter). I removed the member declaration as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181780" author="thw" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 02:25:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rebased patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181997" author="azaroth" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 15:46:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch looks good.&lt;br/&gt;
Committed to trunk.&lt;br/&gt;
Is there a compelling reason to put the patch also in the 0.10 branch?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note: Hive version bumped from 0.4.1 to 0.8 with this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13182000" author="azaroth" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 15:51:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I forgot to say: feel free to reopen the issue if you feel this patch is needed in the 0.10 branch.&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks Thomas!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13182029" author="thw" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 17:11:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Gianmarco - please commit to 0.10 also, we have seen intermittent issues with the hive download that fail our 0.9 and 0.10 CI builds, so we would like to have this change in the branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13182091" author="daijy" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 20:49:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also commit to 0.9/0.10 as per Thomas request.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
